\c 19
\s Mugove waSimioni
\p
\v 1 Mugove wechipiri wakapiwa Simioni, irwo rudzi rwavana vaSimioni nemhuri dzavo; nhaka yavo yakanga iri pakati penhaka yavana vaJudha.
\v 2 Panhaka yavo vakanga vane Bheeri-shebha, kana Shebha, neMoradha,
\v 3 neHazari-shuari, neBhara, neEzemi,
\v 4 neEritoradhi, neBheturi, neHoma,
\v 5 neZikiragi, neBheti-marikabhoti, neHazari-susa,
\v 6 neBheti-rebhaoti, neSharuheni; maguta ane gumi namatatu nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 7 Aini, neRimoni, neEteri, neAshani; maguta mana nemisha yawo ;
\v 8 misha yose yakapoteredza maguta iwayo kusvikira paBhaarati-bheeri, raiva Rama rezasi. Ndiyo yakanga iri nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaSimioni nemhuri dzavo.
\v 9 Nhaka yavana vaSimioni yakanga yato rwa pamugove wavana vaJudha, nekuti mugove wavana vaJudha wakange uri mukurusa; naizvozvo vana vaSimioni vakapiwa nhaka pakati penhaka yavo.
\s Nhaka yaZebhuruni
\p
\v 10 Mugove wechitatu wakapiwa vana vaZebhuruni, nemhuri dzavo; muganhu wenhaka yavo wakasvika paSaridhi.
\p
\v 11 Muganhu wavo wakakwira kumavirazuva, kusvikira paMarara, ndokusvikira paDhabhesheti, ndokusvikira kurukova rwaiva pamberi peJokineamu;
\v 12 kubva paSaridhi wakadzokera kumabvazuva, kunobuda zuva, kusvikira kumuganhu weKisiroti-tabhori, ndokubudira kuDhabherati, ndokukwira Jafia;
\v 13 kubva ipapo wakapfuura kumabvazuva uchienda Gatiheferi, kusvikira paEti-kazini, ndokuguma paRimoni, rinosvika paNea;
\v 14 zvino muganhu ndokudzoka kurutivi rwokumusoro, ndokuenda Hanatoni, ndokuguma pamupata weIfitaeri;
\v 15 neKatati, neNaharari, neShimuroni, neIdhara, neBheterehemu; maguta ane gumi namaviri nemisha yawo.
\v 16 Ndiyo yakanga iri nhaka yavana vaZebhuruni, nemhuri dzavo, maguta iwayo nemisha yawo.
\s Nhaka yaIsakari
\p
\v 17 Mugove wechina wakapiwa Isakari, ivo vana vaIsakari, nemhuri dzavo.
\v 18 Muganhu wavo wakasvika paJezireeri, neKesuroti, neShunemi,
\v 19 neHafaraimi, neShioni, neAnaharoti,
\v 20 neRabhiti, neKishioni, neEbhesi,
\v 21 neRemeti, neEniganimi, neEni-hadha, neBheti-pazezi;
\p
\v 22 muganhu ukasvika paTabhori, neShahazuma, neBheti-shemeshi; muganhu ndokugumira paJorodhani; maguta ane gumi namatanhatu nemisha yawo.
\p
\v 23 Ndiyo yakanga iri nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaIsakari nemhuri dzavo, maguta nemisha yawo.
\s Nhaka yaAsheri
\p
\v 24 Mugove wechishanu wakapiwa rudzi rwavana vaAsheri nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 25 Muganhu wavo wakange uri: Harakati, neHari, neBheteni, neAkishafi,
\p
\v 26 neMamereki, neAmadhi, neMishari, ndokusvikira paKarimeri kumavirazuva, nokuShihori-ribhinati;
\v 27 ndokudzokera kumabvazuva kuBheti-dhagoni ndokusvikira kwaZebhuruni, nokumupata weIfitaeri kumusoro, kusvikira paBheti-emeki, neNeyeri, nokubudira paKabhuri kuruboshwe,
\v 28 neEbhuroni, neRehobhi, neHamoni, neKana, kusvikira paZidhoni guru;
\v 29 zvino muganhu ndokudzokera kuRama, nokuguta reTire rakakombwa norusvingo; muganhu ndokudzokera Hosa, ndokuguma pagungwa panyika yeAkizibhi;
\v 30 uye Uma, neAfeki, neRehobhi; maguta makumi maviri namaviri nemisha yawo.
\v 31 Ndiyo yakanga iri nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaAsheri, nemhuri dzavo maguta iwaya nemisha yawo.
\s Nhaka yaNafutari
\p
\v 32 Mugove wechitanhatu wakapiwa vana vaNafutari, ivo vana vaNafutari nemhuri dzavo.
\v 33 Muganhu wavo wakabva paHerefi, kubva pamuouki weZaananimi, neAdhami-nekebhi, neJabhuneeri, kusvikira paRakumi, ndokuguma paJorodhani;
\v 34 ipapo muganhu wakadzoka kumabvazuva, ndokuenda Azinoti-tabhori; ndokubvapo, ndokuenda Hukoki; ndokusvika kwaZebhuruni kurutivi rwezasi, ndokusvika kwaAsheri kumavirazuva, ndokusvika kwaJudha paJorodhani kumabvazuva.
\v 35 Maguta akanga akakombwa namasvingo akanga ari Zidhimu, neZera, neHamati, neRakati, neKinereti,
\v 36 neAdhama, neRama, neHazori,
\v 37 neKedheshi, neEdhirei, neEni-harori,
\v 38 neIroni, neMigadhari-eri, neHoremu, neBheti-anati, neBheti-shemeshi; maguta ane gumi namapfumbamwe, nemisha yawo.
\v 39 Ndiyo yakanga iri nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaNafutari nemhuri dzavo, maguta iwaya nemisha yawo.
\s Nhaka yaDhani
\p
\v 40 Mugove wechinomwe wakapiwa rudzi rwavana vaDhani nemhuri dzavo.
\v 41 Muganhu wenhaka yavo wakange uri Zora, neEshitaori, neIri-shemeshi;
\v 42 neShaarabhini, neAjaroni, neItira,
\v 43 neEroni, neTimuna, neEkironi,
\v 44 neEriteke, neGibhetoni, neBhaarati,
\v 45 neJehudhi, neBheni-bheraki, neGati-rimoni,
\v 46 neMejarikoni, neRakoni, nenyika yakatarisana neJopa.
\v 47 Asi nyika yavana vaDhani yakanga iri dukusa; naizvozvo vana vaDhani vakandorwa neReshemi, vakarikunda, vakariparadza neminondo inopinza, vakapiwa guta iro, vakagaramo; vakatumidza Reshemi zita rinonzi Dhani, zita rababa vavo Dhani.
\v 48 Ndiyo yakanga iri
\p nhaka yorudzi rwavana vaDhani nemhuri dzavo, namaguta iwaya nemisha yawo.
\s Joshua unopiwa Timunati-sera
\p
\v 49 Naizvozvo vakapedza kugovera nyika, yakanga iri nhaka yavo nemiganhu yayo; vana vaIsiraeri vakapa Joshua mwanakomana waNuni nhaka yake pakati pavo;
\v 50 sezvavakanga varairwa naJehovha, vakamupa guta raakakumbira, Timunati-sera, panyika yamakomo yaEfuremu; akavaka guta iro, akagaramo.
\p
\v 51 Ndidzo nhaka dzakagoverwa nemijenya paShiro pamberi paJehovha, pamukova wetende rokusangana, nomupristi Ereazari, naJoshua mwanakomana waNuni, navakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba amarudzi avana valsiraeri, kuti dzive nhaka dzavo. Naizvozvo vakapedza kugovera nyika.
